   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"To Dionysios, one of those of equal rank with the First Friends, and strategos, from Aphynchis son of Ptolemaios, resident of Euhemeria in the Themistes meris. I have brought a second petition against Ptolemaios, my younger brother, and his wife . . ."</ab>
